                       ===========================================
                       TV Program Scheduler/Recorder Scripts Suite
                       ===========================================

======
Setup
======

# systemctl enable atd

=============
Run Scheduler
=============
# ./tv-sch.sh 2021-05-21 21:00 95m 65 音速小子
# ./tv-sch-D.sh 12:00 60m 10 中視午間新聞

==============
Check Schedule
==============
atq
at -c 5		# show the detail of job 5
